To connect to database, you will need to change connection string  in App.config of SQLLite to point to the TestDB.db file.
For some reaon it need to be a  UNC path to the database file.
Example.
</configSections>
    <connectionStrings>
    <add name="DBSQLite" connectionString="Data Source=C:\Users\Tom\Desktop\ToDoListApp\TestDB.db" providerName="System.Data.SQLite"/>
</connectionStrings>  
